metadata.name: Degenerational Wealth
metadata.description:
It is the middle ground between pen and paper, between dreams and reality, and it lies between the pit of ridiculousness and the summit of absurdity. This is the dimension of creation. It is the area we call LMBO.

This first piece introduces an entirely new piece of art for me. LMBO will be an evolution of my creations.

Created in Procreate / Tracked Time: 60hrs / Size: 5607 x 4000px / File / Type: PNG / Date Created: 09.30.22
